<h3 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Non-FunctionalRequirementsTr=
aceability">Non-Functional Requirements Traceability</h3>
<p>NFRs for Account listing/ Account detail:</p>
<p><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/Non-Functi=
onal+Requirements+-+Channels+Squad+NFRs#NonFunctionalRequirementsChannelsSq=
uadNFRs-Performanceperbusinessactivity-MVP" rel=3D"nofollow">Non-Functional=
 Requirements - Channels Squad NFRs - Westpac One Core - Westpac Enterprise=
 Confluence</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Data retention:</p>
<p>As per ACD the data retention for Past account data / transactions is 25=
 months. (the UI should also limit query data older than 25 months)</p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Below is an estimation of storage size consumed in Redis: (Expiry/TTL TB=
C)</p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Assume we store&nbsp;<strong>7 years of daily data per account</strong>:=
</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><strong>Size per balance object</strong>: ~228 bytes</li>
<li><strong>Total balance objects</strong>: <br><span class=3D"katex-displa=
y"><span class=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml">10,000 accounts=C3=97=
365 days/year=C3=977 years=3D25,550,000 objects</span></span></span></li>
<li><strong>Estimated Redis store size</strong>: <br><span class=3D"katex-d=
isplay"><span class=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml">25,550,000=C3=97=
228~5,825,400,000 bytes~5.43 GB</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-12360171" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-12360171" cla=
ss=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-12360171"=
 class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expand=
ed=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-12360171"><span class=3D"expa=
nd-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=3D"t=
rue"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Example o=
bject</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-12360171" class=3D"expand-conte=
nt" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-12360171">
