<h2 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-TechnicalDebt">Technical Deb=
t</h2>
<p></p>
<p>N/A</p>
<h1 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Solution"><span>Solution</sp=
an></h1>
<h2 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-SolutionOverview"><span>Solu=
tion Overview</span></h2>
<p>To enhance the customer experience, the accounts list and activity pages=
 will be uplifted to support viewing past account balances and transaction =
summaries. A new "as at" date selector will be added to the accounts list p=
age, allowing users to view end-of-day balances from ATLAS for past dates, =
while current balances will continue to be sourced from 10x. Redis will be =
used to cache historical data by account and date, with INF APIs enriching =
the cache when needed. The export to CSV will include these past balances.<=
/p>
<p>On the account activity page, users will be able to view opening and clo=
sing balances, total credits and debits, and end-of-day balances for select=
ed dates or ranges. Additionally, the interest and tax tab will show accrue=
d debit and credit interest for the current month, calculated daily but pos=
ted monthly.</p>
<p>These enhancements will rely on data from 10x, ATLAS, Redis, and INF API=
s, as summarised at the table below:&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table id=3D"TBL1773175605611" class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTa=
ble" style=3D"width: 91.9448%;" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers" data-sn=
ooker-locked-cols=3D"0">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 1.81594%;">
<col style=3D"width: 55.6678%;">
<col style=3D"width: 22.3531%;">
<col style=3D"width: 20.1631%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh" scope=3D"col" contenteditable=3D=
"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false"><br></th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Description&nbsp;</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Notes / Impact Analysis&nbsp;</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Dependency</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;">Uplift the<span>&=
nbsp;</span><strong>accounts list</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>page - enable =
customer users to see past account balances</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>Add a new 'as at' date selection on the accounts list page</li>
<li><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"a793fd73-284d-4379-85=
04-9794f63dcd09">When the page first loads, by default the account list sho=
ws the account balances as of now (real time) - no change from existing exp=
erience</span></li>
<li><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"a793fd73-284d-4379-85=
04-9794f63dcd09">If user selects a date in the past then they will see the =
"end of day balance" as at the past date</span>
<ul>
<li>Note that 10x doesn't have the concept of a closing balance so it would=
 be the end of day balance at 11:59pm</li>
</ul></li>
<li>The existing export to CSV capability should now include the new past b=
alance data</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>Account listing EXP</strong> endpoint=
 to&nbsp;</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>retrieve past data from ATLAS if past dates are selected in the search =
criteria.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
<li>retrieve current data from existing Account listing route (i.e. <a href=
=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcadm-proddealacct=
adm-instl-arrngmntsvcng-v1?tab=3Ddetail" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nof=
ollow">w1c arrangement endpoint</a>)</li>
<li>retrieve past data from new Opening/closing balance route (i.e. <a href=
=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcadm-proddealacct=
adm-instl-arrngmntsvcng-v1?tab=3Ddetail" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nof=
ollow">w1c arrangement endpoint</a>)</li>
<li>store past data in Redis.&nbsp;</li>
<li>aggregate data from Redis (if any) with the current data and response a=
s an aggregated list to user.</li>
</ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Redis </strong>to cache by Account with data con=
taining</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>As of date</li>
<li>Account balance&nbsp;</li>
</ul><p>if (user selected as of date &gt; last cached date)</p><p>&nbsp; ca=
ll INF API to cache extra data</p><p>otherwise&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;get all da=
ta from Redis</p><p><br></p>
<ol>
<li>Definition of balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>as-is=20
<ol>
<li>Current balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>current balance in 10x (Posted balance in 10x, uncleared funds is not a=
pplicable to w1c at the moment)</li>
</ol></li>
<li>Available balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>current balance + IDOL limits + Overdraft Limits (Calculated in WASH la=
yer)</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li>to be&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>Current date (default)=20
<ol>
<li>current balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>Same as as-is current balance</li>
</ol></li>
<li>available balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>Same as as-is available balance</li>
</ol></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(24,27,37);">closing balance</span>
<ol>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(24,27,37);">T-1 data coming from ATLAS</span>=
</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
<li>Past date is selected&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>current balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>Same as as-is current balance</li>
</ol></li>
<li>available balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>Same as as-is available balance</li>
</ol></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(24,27,37);">closing </span>balance&nbsp;=20
<ol>
<li>T-N end of day balance in ATLAS</li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></li>
</ol></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><s>Devops</s></li>
</ul>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><s>10x&nbsp;</s></li>
<li>ATLAS</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">2</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;">Uplift the<span>&=
nbsp;</span><strong>account activity<span>&nbsp;</span></strong>page - enab=
le customer users to see past account balances and total credits &amp; debi=
ts</p>
<ul class=3D"alternate" style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>Introduce new info to the account activity page to show the following d=
ata for today (default), a past selected day or a date range period:=20
<ul class=3D"alternate">
<li>Opening balance</li>
<li>Total <s>number and</s> value of credits</li>
<li>Total <s>number and</s> value of debits</li>
</ul></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">If a past day is selected, also show=
 the end of day balance for the account</span></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><strong>New EXP APIs</strong> to=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>retrieve total debits/credits</li>
<li>retrieve opening/closing balance</li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p><br></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>uplift&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-=
prodsvcadm-proddealacctadm-instl-arrngmntsvcng-v1?tab=3Ddetail" class=3D"ex=
ternal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">w1c arrangement endpoint </a>to retrieve:=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>opening balance (as of start date range)</li>
<li>closing balance (as of end date range)</li>
</ul></li>
<li>uplift&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/AR=
TC/Transaction+Listing+Information+API" rel=3D"nofollow">instl account tran=
sactions </a>endpoint to retrieve&nbsp;<br>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Total value of credits&nbsp;</li>
<li>Total value of debits</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Devops</li>
<li>ATLAS</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">3</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">&nbsp;Uplift the&nbsp;<strong style=3D"text-alig=
n: left;">account activity&nbsp;</strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77=
);">page -&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">Show</span><s=
pan style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&nbsp;</span><strong style=3D"letter-s=
pacing: 0.0px;">accrued debit &amp; credit interest</strong><span style=3D"=
letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&nbsp;</span><strong style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px=
;">for the current month</strong><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">, s=
o that an organisation can see the interest accrual that hasn't been posted=
 yet.</span><p style=3D"text-align: left;">Note that the way interest works=
 is:&nbsp;Interest is calculated and accrued daily but is only posted/charg=
ed to the account once a month (usually on the 1st day of the next month)</=
p><p style=3D"text-align: left;">There's no value in seeing accrued interes=
t for the past, because the user can view posted interest transactions inst=
ead.</p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p><p style=3D"text-align: left=
;">Scope</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>Add accrued interest to the account activity interest and tax tab</li>
<li>This should be a sum of the interest accrued per day, since 1st day of =
the month until today (it resets on the 1st day of every month)</li>
<li>Both debit and credit accruals should be shown</li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li><strong>New EXP APIs</strong> to=20
<ul>
<li>retrieve accrued credit/debit interest&nbsp;</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/pages/viewpage.action?=
pageId=3D1947332258" rel=3D"nofollow">GTS inf API</a> to=20
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>retrieve accrued credit/debit interest since last posting date until to=
day (DTD refer to <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/pages/vi=
ewpage.action?pageId=3D1947332258" rel=3D"nofollow">Account Interest &amp; =
Tax Details Information API - Westpac One Core - Westpac Enterprise Conflue=
nce</a> )</li>
<li>Support for accrued interest for current FY to be added in Feb 2026</li=
>
<li>INF API uplift should be finished in Feb 2026 and it's just an uplift f=
or EXP API and UI</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>Devops</li>
<li>ATLAS</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">4</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">5</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
