<h2 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-API">API</h2>
<ol>
<li><h4 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Opening/ClosingbalanceIN=
FAPI">Opening / Closing balance INF API</h4>
<ol>
<li><h5 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Examplerequest">Example =
request</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Request</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">POST /bal=
ances/accountIds?filterDateTime=3D2018-12-29T03:16:42.254Z,2019-01-29T03:16=
:42.254Z
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountIds": [
    {
      "BSB": "035845",
      "accountNumber": "10235674897"
    }
  ]
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><h5 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Exampleresponse(response=
shouldalwayscontainonerecord/accountduetotheBR#2.whichistoreturnoneopening/=
closingbalanceforagivendaterange.BR#1isjustextendingtherequirementbyallowin=
galistofaccountsasinputandrespondingwithalis">Example response (response sh=
ould always contain one record / account due to the BR#2. which is to retur=
n one opening/closing balance for a given date range. BR#1 is just extendin=
g the requirement by allowing a list of accounts as input and responding wi=
th a list of objects each correspond to one account id)</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Response</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": {
    "balances": [
      {
        "accountId": {
          "BSB": "035845",
          "accountNumber": "10235674897"
        },
        "openingBalance": {
          "amount": "1500.75",
          "currencyCode": "AUD",
          "position": "CR"
        },
        "closingBalance": {
          "amount": "1750.25",
          "currencyCode": "AUD",
          "position": "CR"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol></li>
<li><h4 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Totaldebit/creditINFAPI"=
>Total debit / credit INF API</h4>
<ol>
<li><h5 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Examplerequest.1">Exampl=
e request</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Request</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">POST /tra=
nsactions/accountId/debitCredit?filterDateTime=3D2018-12-29T03:16:42.254Z,2=
019-01-29T03:16:42.254Z
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": {
    "BSB": "035845",
    "accountNumber": "10235674897"
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><h5 id=3D"id-12.SD:PastaccountbalancesChannels-Exampleresponse">Example=
 response</h5>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;"><b>Response</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": {
    "accountId": {
      "BSB": "035845",
      "accountNumber": "10235674897"
    },
    "totalDebit": {
      "amount": "500.00",
      "currencyCode": "AUD"
    },
    "totalCredit": {
      "amount": "1200.00",
      "currencyCode": "AUD"
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
